00:10:54.885 --> 00:11:00.885
The next critical step in an interaction is how you respond to the user's questions.

193
00:11:00.885 --> 00:11:05.385
If they're taking the time to explain to you what happened, but you brush off their concerns

194
00:11:05.385 --> 00:11:09.425
